{
  "texts": [
    "➢ Which are the top-cited articles in this domain and what insights do they provide into the impact and influence of AI in public services?",
    "➢ What are the predominant trends in the use of AI within public services, as evidenced by the literature published between 1984 and 2023?",
    "To address these research questions, a bibliometric analysis was performed using the Scopus database, covering global literature from 1984 to 2023.",
    "The systematic search, conducted on November 30, 2023, employed a comprehensive query focused on key terms related to AI and public services.",
    "The inclusion criteria were established to include articles, conference papers, and book chapters published in English."
  ]
}